meta {
  name: Resolver
  seq: 8
}

docs {
  Public QR-scan resolver — a SEPARATE binary on port 8081 ({{resolverUrl}}), not the api.
  Run it too: `cargo run -p electronix-id-resolver`. If it is not running, every request here
  fails with a connection error (not an assertion failure). These use {{publicCode}} captured by
  Create Machine / Rotate Tag. Runs before Cleanup so the machine still exists.
}
